<p begin="00:05:44.077" end="00:05:47.581" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">&gt;&gt; Jon: SO SHE WAS FATALLISTIC<br/>ABOUT WHAT HAPPENED TO HER.</span></p>
